I expect I will stay a few more days here at this hotel. There is no hurry. I could have stayed in Nicaragua and got to Costa Rica quicker but this is a chance to experience new culture. Don’t forget, Costa Rica was the first place I visited in Central America. It has been good to be here and especially in the Guanacaste province.

Buenos dias, and Talk to you soon…

J W Bull

The statistics show that there are more accidents involving car or truck collisions in Costa Rica than in the United States of America each year. Of course, the size of the country is tiny so the percentage is still high. Another factor is that Costa Rica has far fewer vehicles on its roads compared to the United States. It’s important that you are fully covered and protected when you hit the road here in Costa Rica.

There are four coverage’s. The most important is called liability. It is that portion of the coverage that compensates the other party for harms and losses suffered as a consequence of a car accident. The insurance company does not pay first.
